---
import PageHeading from "../components/page-heading.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <section class="relative z-20 max-w-2xl mx-auto my-12 px-7 lg:px-0">
    <PageHeading
      title="About Me"
      description="Hello 👋 I'm KeMiao, a student from Nanjing, China. I'm passionate about programming and sharing resources."
    />

    <!-- GIF 部分 -->
    <div class="relative z-30 w-full my-10 text-center">
      <a href="https://blog-v3.kemeow.top/">
        <img 
          src="https://media.giphy.com/media/SWoSkN6DxTszqIKEqv/giphy.gif" 
          alt="GIF Link" 
          class="mx-auto rounded-xl"
          style="max-height: 275px;"
        />
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- 波浪标题部分 -->
    <div class="my-10 text-center">
      <img 
        src="https://capsule-render.vercel.app/api?type=waving&color=timeGradient&height=150&&section=header&text=HI%20THERE!&fontSize=50&fontAlign=50&fontAlignY=30&desc=I%20AM%20KeMiao%20%F0%9F%91%8B&descAlign=50&descSize=20&descAlignY=50&animation=twinkling" 
        alt="Waving Capsule"
        class="mx-auto"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- 动态打字效果 -->
    <div class="my-6 text-center">
      <img 
        src="https://readme-typing-svg.demolab.com?font=Fira+Code&size=20&pause=1000&center=true&vCenter=true&width=500&lines=Welcome+to+my+About+page!;I+am+KeMiao+who+loves+programming!" 
        alt="Typing Effect"
        class="mx-auto"
      />
    </div>

    <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">Short Bio</h2>
    <ul class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg list-disc pl-5">
      <li class="py-1">🔭 I'm currently studying in Nanjing</li>
      <li class="py-1">🌱 Current learning: Automation Technology and Applications, front-end development</li>
      <li class="py-1">💬 Ask me about resources</li>
      <li class="py-1">📫 Contact: <a href="mailto:kemiaofx@163.com" class="text-indigo-600 underline">kemiaofx@163.com</a></li>
      <li class="py-1">🍉 Communities: 
        <a href="https://blog-v3.kemeow.top" class="text-indigo-600 underline">BLOG</a> | 
        <a href="https://t.me/KemiaoJun" class="text-indigo-600 underline">Telegram</a> | 
        <a href="https://x.com/kemiaosw/" class="text-indigo-600 underline">X</a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-2 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">Personal Introduction</h2>
    <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg">
      大家好！这里是克喵爱吃卤面的博客。致力于分享资源、生活日记和踩坑教程，代码水准一般，自动化专业大二学生，现于南京就读，普通的大学牛马。
    </p>
    <div class="mt-4 flex gap-4">
      <a href="https://kemiao.online" class="text-indigo-600 underline">个人主页</a>
      <a href="https://blog-v3.kemeow.top" class="text-indigo-600 underline">博客站点</a>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-2 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">About Me</h2>
    <ul class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg list-disc pl-5">
      <li class="py-1">🖥 <strong>个性:</strong> 开朗活泼，热爱学习，勤奋工作</li>
      <li class="py-1">🖥 <strong>技能:</strong> 自动化技术与应用</li>
      <li class="py-1">🖥 <strong>个人信息:</strong>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-1">
          <li class="py-1">🧑 <strong>姓名:</strong> mcy</li>
          <li class="py-1">🏫 <strong>学校:</strong> <a href="https://www.niit.edu.cn/" class="text-indigo-600 underline">南京工业职业技术大学</a></li>
          <li class="py-1">🏛️ <strong>年级:</strong> 大二</li>
          <li class="py-1">👷 <strong>职业:</strong> 学生</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li class="py-1">🖥 <strong>兴趣:</strong> 计算机，单机游戏，电子产品，数码产品，资源分享</li>
      <li class="py-1">🖥 <strong>梦想:</strong> 咸鱼算不算？</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-4 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">GitHub Stats</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
      <img 
        src="https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api?username=Kemeow815&show_icons=true&theme=transparent" 
        alt="GitHub Stats" 
        class="w-full rounded-lg"
      />
      <img 
        src="https://github-readme-activity-graph.vercel.app/graph?username=Kemeow815&theme=github-compact&radius=16&height=300" 
        alt="Activity Graph" 
        class="w-full rounded-lg"
      />
      <img 
        src="https://github-immortality.vercel.app/api?username=Kemeow815" 
        alt="修仙系列统计卡片" 
        class="w-full rounded-lg"
      />
    </div>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-2 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">Support</h2>
    <ul class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg list-disc pl-5">
      <li class="py-1">
        微信公众号: <a href="https://wechat.kemeow.top/" class="text-indigo-600 underline">克喵的小站</a>
      </li>
      <li class="py-1">
        赞助页面: <a href="https://donate.kemeow.top/" class="text-indigo-600 underline">点我</a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-2 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">Let's Connect</h2>
    <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg">
      Feel free to reach out via <a href="mailto:kemiaofx@163.com" class="text-indigo-600 underline">email</a> or 
      follow me on <a href="https://x.com/kemiaosw/" class="text-indigo-600 underline">X</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
